---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="支持光禾 | 光禾華德福">
  <Navigation />
  
  <section class="hero-small">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>支持光禾</h1>
      <p>感謝您對華德福教育的支持</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-block">
        <p>感謝您對光華華德福實驗學校的支持！您的捐助將用於：</p>
        <ul>
          <li>學校永續發展</li>
          <li>教師培訓計畫</li>
          <li>學生學習環境改善</li>
          <li>各項教育活動舉辦</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bank-card">
        <h2>🏦 學校常用帳號</h2>
        <div class="bank-info">
          <div class="bank-item">
            <h3>銀行代號：007（第一銀行-五甲分行）</h3>
            <p>銀行帳號：720-10-656226</p>
            <p>戶 名：光禾華德福實驗學校</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bank-card">
        <h2>📋 專款專用帳號</h2>
        <div class="bank-info">
          <div class="bank-item">
            <h3>🌟 學校永續發展基金專戶(學校)</h3>
            <p>銀行代號：007（第一銀行-五甲分行）</p>
            <p>銀行帳號：720-10-658911</p>
            <p>戶 名：光禾華德福實驗學校</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bank-item">
            <h3>🌟 教師培訓計畫發展基金專戶(學校)</h3>
            <p>銀行代號：007（第一銀行-五甲分行）</p>
            <p>銀行帳號：720-10-658920</p>
            <p>戶 名：光禾華德福實驗學校</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bank-item">
            <h3>🌟 家長互助專車專戶(協會)</h3>
            <p>銀行代號：006（合作金庫-七賢分行）</p>
            <p>銀行帳號：5252-717-323561</p>
            <p>戶 名：社團法人高雄市華德福教育協會</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="notice">
        <p>💚 感謝您的愛心支持！</p>
        <p>如有問題請聯絡我們：07-7885128</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2026 光禾華德福實驗學校. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-small {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C00, #FFD700);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-small h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
  .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .intro-block {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139,69,19,0.1);
  }

  .intro-block p { color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  
  .intro-block ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #666; }
  .intro-block li { padding: 0.5rem 0; }

  .bank-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139,69,19,0.1);
  }

  .bank-card h2 { color: #8B4513; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #e0d4c8; }

  .bank-item {
    background: #FFF8DC;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .bank-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .bank-item h3 { color: #228B22; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .bank-item p { color: #666; margin: 0.3rem 0; }

  .notice {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #228B22, #8B4513);
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .notice p { margin: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .footer { background: #333; color: white; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; }
</style>
